27
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:05,159
(Su Mu, General)

28
00:02:05,159 --> 00:02:06,760
That's my daughter.

29
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:08,120
You've surpassed me.

30
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,199
