37
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:27,919
Yan,

38
00:02:29,159 --> 00:02:29,759
your illness

39
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,919
can be cured now.

40
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,719
(Outskirts of Nanyuan Nation)
Come on. It's so easy to get this money.

41
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:37,080
Jiang Beimo has been appointed
the top scholar

42
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,479
and will come to marry you tomorrow.

43
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:41,080
