45
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:48,759
(Father, can my illness
really be cured?)

46
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:09,800
(Now this medicine lacks
only one core ingredient)

47
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,000
(to be complete.)

48
00:03:30,035 --> 00:03:33,824
