to practice martial arts.

75
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:32,560
Now the time of the hostage's return
is approaching.

76
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:35,360
Various powers are targeting him.

77
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:38,279
